) that manages offline"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"}}}